{
  "stem": "15014.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how do you call this, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that kills you-- came from the-- Bullet?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bullet came into our-- I was-- we were sitting next to the table, eating something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the bullet came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know that this was bullet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I, I felt wind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my hair was cut like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we looked at the-- at the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we take out the bullet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this-- what I consider luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, related to all that, you were saying earlier, before the interview, that some of the Schindler testimonies or stories weren't entirely, you know, legitimate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bah, the people forgot, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not going to elaborate on that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Don't expect me to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I won't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I won't explain it because it's nothing to explain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, some people don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people trying to put-- let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are some people that I wouldn't care to associate with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if these people will read this, they will know whom I am talking about, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this is not such a-- such a thing that I am going to be very proud.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I met, you know, somebody that--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--at the party in Syracuse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, he's going--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's, you know, this guy-- I just read-- is today, on this committee, on that committee, this-- you know, and he was the one that wanted to put me to death.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If my husband wouldn't tell me 'jump,' I wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the people was doing many things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Marcel, Marcel Goldberg-- and, and he took so much money from the people to put them on the list.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
